mportant and meaningful financial goalsbring effective risk mitigation strategies to independent financial advisors and their clients in order to help them protect the wealth they have builthelp financial advisors build elite and highly successful businesses through our expert insights training and consulting in all major areas of practice managementdeliver effective retirement income strategies that are built to address the challenges of historically low interest rates and rising life expectanciesgoalsbased investment managementhorizon’s goalsbased strategies are designed to provide an allimportant direct link between investment strategies and clients’ key objectives this link enables clients to address the three distinct stages throughout their investment lifecyclegainclients seek to grow wealth so it can support and enhance their most important life goalsprotectclients seek to guard wealth against catastrophic losses that could jeopardize their financial securityspendclients seek to ensure that their wealth is there for them during what may be lengthy and active retirementshorizon investments helps advisors build and manage entrepreneurial advisory businesses our experience encompasses every aspect of owning operating and building a financial advisory business—wealth management financial planning investment management client relationship management client acquisition marketing technology staffing and succession we offer this knowledge to our advisor clients through a comprehensive suite of education training and consulting solutions through our experienced team of advisor consulting associateschoose an option below to learn moreadvisorsinvestors  horizon investments was founded in  as an independent financial advisory firm serving individuals and families in the columbia south carolina area since that time working directly with investors we have expanded our mission and capabilitiestoday with headquarters in charlotte north carolina horizon provides comprehensive investment and practice management solutions to independent financial advisors across the country the firm was recognized in  and  for growth and innovation by money management institute and has received numerous industry commendations for its investment management expertise  we know advisors because we are advisors everything we do at horizon is designed to help our fellow advisors deliver a superior experience to their clients and build successful businesses our deep roots in the financial advisory world mean we understand the issues that financial advisors care about the challenges that financial advisors worry about and the resources that financial advisors must seek out to achieve success for their clients their teams their partners and themselveswe are a community of professionals working together in an effort to provide bestinclass financial services and superior customer service to our clients the unique blend of professionals within our investment team provides a variety of skill sets and experience that allows us to balance quantitative diligence with qualitative wisdominvestmentsrobbie cannonrobbie cannonpresident  ceorobbie cannon is the president and ceo of horizon investments llc which specializes in active asset allocation risk mitigation and retirement income during his tenure which began in  horizon has grown from a small retail ria firm to a multibillion dollar thirdparty investment management group with a national footprint of independent broker dealers and institutional clients his career in finance began in  and has encompassed various aspects of portfolio management including asset allocation equity analysis and risk management he graduated from furman university and lives in charlotte nc mr cannon is a national speaker on topics from asset allocation and risk management to market dynamicsron saba cfaron saba cfasenior managing director of investment managementwith three decades of investment management experience mr saba he is responsible for